	   <tr><td colspan=2>I've doubled with enchanters before at around lvl 15 or so, and we would tag team the mobs.&nbsp;&nbsp;I mean charm is a hard spell to use, but with another chanter helping you keep the mob under control it becomes easy, someone cast tash, then someone charm (whoever has higher charisma)  if charm breaks chanter 1 meses to stop the attack while chanter 2 recharms.  Helped us take out a derv camp pretty easily with minimum hp loss (we only get attacked when the charm wears off).<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
