	   <tr><td colspan=2>This trick can be done a lot easier by holding down the forward button and the left or right button while using mouse-look to control your direction.&nbsp;&nbsp;With a little practice it will become a natural option in times where panic has been the ussual reaction.<br><br>Thanks to Thirstar on Erollisi Marr For the many times it saved me.<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
