	   <tr><td colspan=2>I see such a waste in one of the greatest power enchanters commonly do not use. CHARM. This method requires you have faith in your healer. Basically, Head into a dungeon and charm a nuker for HOURS at a time. This charm will do twice the damage of any tanks in your group and is easy to keep. First, mem the lvl 4 mez spell you probably never use and load up charm. Once you find your target Mez, Tash Charm. Keep pet hotkeys avail at all time and a AOE stun up for when charm breaks. If it does, Stun, (tash if necessary), mez, and charm again. The lvl 4 mez only last 30 secs and if your chrisma is very high this charm can last quite a long time. I would not recommend this until your over lvl 35 and can afford to keep Rune up alot.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
