	   <tr><td colspan=2>Short note, less experienced players or ignorant ones make crowd control difficult.&nbsp;&nbsp;If you cant tutor your group to fight 1 mob at a time quickly, just give up and use charm.  If you keep pestering them, they just think you are a jerk.  At least with charm you reduce crowd by 1 and add to group by 1... not a bad change in odds.  Just my opinion.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
