	   <tr><td colspan=2>I soloed in Lake of Ill Omen off and on from 23-29 and i found charming to be a great strategy i could usually kill 3 mobs and still be at 40% and i managed to kill a string of 6 mobs on one bar of mana at 27, needless to say, amazing XP =)<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
